------------------------------------------------------------

Now, about arrangement of electromagnets.
Sphere for easier calculation and symmetry. Apparently 
not latitude and longitude because magnets cluster near
the pole. 
Recommended:
Fibonnacci sphere -> geodesic sphere
and N=32 electromagnets, not too small (N<12 control authority
becomes poor) but not too large (N>64 not yet, not until
model is stable).
